保罗·希顿表示，如果艺术家想在票价上为粉丝提供“优惠”，他们就需要“在场” https://www.nme.com/news/music/paul-heaton-artists-need-to-be-in-the-room-good-deal-for-fans-on-ticket-prices-3801788?utm_source= rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=保罗·希顿艺术家需要在房间里为粉丝提供优惠门票价格Daniel PetersFri, 11 Oct 2024 10:14:39 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndieLive Music NewsRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3801788 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Heaton@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="保罗·希顿在英国音乐节的舞台上表演" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Heaton@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Heaton@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Heaton@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Heaton@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Heaton@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Heaton@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他补充说，艺术家应该参加“会议来决定票价、实际费用”以及“是否有动态定价”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paul-heaton-artists-need-to-be-in-the-room-good-deal-for-fans-on-ticket-prices-3801788">保罗·希顿 (Paul Heaton) 表示，如果艺术家想要为粉丝提供“优惠”的票价，他们就需要“在场”，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Heaton@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="保罗·希顿在英国音乐节的舞台上表演" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Heaton@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Heaton@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Heaton@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Heaton@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Heaton@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Heaton@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paul-heaton">保罗·希顿</a>表示，鉴于最近动态的票价争议，如果艺术家希望粉丝们能得到“一笔划算的交易”，他们就需要“在房间里”做出票价决定。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paul-heaton-on-buying-everyone-a-pint-and-why-the-royal-family-is-the-one-thing-worth-privatising-3230442">保罗·希顿（Paul Heaton）谈给每个人买一品脱啤酒以及为什么“王室是值得私有化的”</a></strong></li></ul><p>昨天（10 月 10 日），这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-housemartins">Housemartins</a>前主唱在接受<a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/c361r81lx65o" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>BBC 早餐节目</em></a>采访时表示：“如果你想为粉丝提供优惠，你就必须到场”。</p><p> “虽然我并没有责怪其他艺术家，但我认为如果你想控制它，你就必须参加会议，”他继续说道。 “决定门票价格、实际费用、是否有动态定价的会议。”</p><p> “我代表我自己和我的音乐家，但我也觉得那里没有代表歌迷。所以当我去那里的时候，我总是会想到我认识的人，他们买得起门票吗？”</p><p>今天（10 月 11 日）希顿发行了由 Lightning Seeds 主唱伊恩·布劳迪 (Ian Broudie) 制作的新个人专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paul-heaton-announces-new-ian-broudie-produced-album-the-mighty-several-and-uk-tour-with-the-zutons-3767640">《The Mighty Few》</a> 。 11 月，他将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-zutons">Zutons</a>一起<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paul-heaton-extra-2024-uk-tour-dates-new-special-guests-lightning-seeds-3775345">开始英国头条巡演，</a>同时<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lightning-seeds">Lightning Seeds</a>也将在曼彻斯特为他开场。</p><p>本周早些时候，希顿<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paul-heaton-announces-huge-show-at-sheffields-bramall-lane-with-lightning-seeds-and-shed-seven-buy-tickets-3800284">宣布将于 5 月 25 日在谢菲尔德布拉莫巷体育场（他心爱的谢菲尔德联队的主场）举行一场盛大的演出</a>。</p><p>与他即将在英国举行的其他演出一样，门票将以固定价格出售，体育场演出的票价为 39.50 英镑（另加预订费）—— <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/paul-heaton-tickets/artist/35771?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=QPKyP%3A1lbxyKRfJ0HswJ3TmdUkCUM3wpGVn6y80&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">您可以在这里购买</a>。或者，粉丝可以通过<a href="https://paulheaton.co.uk/#gigs" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处注册</a>进行预售。 </p><figure id="attachment_3800328" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3800328" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3800328" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/PaulHeaton-Sheffield-show.jpg" alt="保罗·希顿在舞台上现场表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/PaulHeaton-Sheffield-show.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/PaulHeaton-Sheffield-show-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/PaulHeaton-Sheffield-show-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/PaulHeaton-Sheffield-show-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/PaulHeaton-Sheffield-show-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/PaulHeaton-Sheffield-show-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3800328" class="wp-caption-text">保罗·希顿现场表演。图片来源：Roberto Ricciuti/Redferns/Getty</figcaption></figure><p>鉴于即将到来的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">绿洲</a>重聚巡演，动态门票定价的话题激增——许多排了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-2025-fans-frustrated-as-theyre-held-in-long-queues-on-ticketmaster-3789320">几个小时的</a>队购买英国巡演日期门票的人失望地发现， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-fans-react-to-ticketmasters-dynamic-pricing-3789361">由于“动态”定价体系</a>。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-gilmour">大卫·吉尔莫（David Gilmour）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artitst/Tom-Walker">汤姆·沃克（Tom Walker）</a>等艺术家曾公开表示，艺术家可以在此事上有发言权，前者表示乐队应该<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/david-gilmour-says-oasis-should-do-exactly-what-they-want-to-but-put-a-price-on-tickets-and-stick-to-it-3792799">“对门票定价并坚持下去”，</a>而后者则表示<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tom-walker-weighs-in-on-oasis-style-dynamic-ticket-pricing-3793278">“如果所有艺术家对因需求旺盛而导致最后一刻门票价格上涨说“不”，这不会是一件事”</a> 。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Iron-Maiden">Iron Maiden</a>还向粉丝承诺，他们即将举行的 2025 年巡演“不会有动态票价”。</p><p>在绿洲乐队确认<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-confirm-dynamic-pricing-will-not-be-applied-to-north-american-reunion-tour-dates-3798327">动态票务系统不会在英国应用</a>后，其美国巡演的票价明显低于向英国歌迷提供的票价。</p><p>另一方面，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/coldplay">酷玩乐队</a>最近宣布了他们的“无限门票”定价计划，粉丝可以以实惠的价格购买他们正在进行的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coldplay-announce-music-of-the-spheres-2025-north-american-tour-buy-tickets-3800743">“Music Of The Spheres”</a>世界巡演的门票。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coldplay-uk-tour-stadium-london-wembley-hull-music-venue-trust-tickets-3794308">他们即将举行的英国体育场演出</a>——包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/coldplay-to-break-taylor-swift-and-take-thats-wembley-stadium-record-with-huge-10-night-run-3797432">在温布利破纪录的 10 晚演出</a>——乐队利润的 10% 将捐献给<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/music-venue-trust-coldplay-ticket-money-donation-interview-3798462">音乐场地信托基金</a>。上个月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sleaford-mods">Sleaford Mods</a>宣布他们将为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sleaford-mods-are-selling-5-uk-tour-tickets-for-people-on-low-incomes-3797112">英国演出提供 5 英镑的门票</a>，特别是针对低收入人群。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paul-heaton-on-buying-everyone-a-pint-and-why-the-royal-family-is-the-one-thing-worth-privatising-3230442">在 2022 年接受<em>NME</em>采访时</a>，直言不讳的希顿还谈到了支持 NHS 的必要性，并且任何私有化的尝试都应该针对其他地方，比如王室。</p><p> “如果这是一个很好的商业模式，那就拥有它。把它卖给日本人、沙特人或者其他什么人，”他告诉<em>《NME》</em> 。 “你知道这些资本家接手后会做什么吗？他们裁掉了所有不需要的员工，只留了一名……”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paul-heaton-artists-need-to-be-in-the-room-good-deal-for-fans-on-ticket-prices-3801788">保罗·希顿 (Paul Heaton) 表示，如果艺术家想要为粉丝提供“优惠”的票价，他们就需要“在场”，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
